---
<div class="clipping-wrap">
  <div class="shadow-card" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <article class="card">
    <header class="card-header">
      <span class="masthead">CityDesk Austin</span>
      <span class="section-label">Home &amp; Property</span>
    </header>
    <p class="byline">By Marcus Webb &middot; Jun 22, 2026</p>
    <h3 class="headline">How Austin Homeowners Are Cutting Summer Cooling Bills in 2026</h3>
    <p class="body-copy">
      With July highs creeping past 100&deg;, local pros say the fix usually isn't a new unit.
      Several Travis County crews now offer same-week tune-ups, and homeowners we spoke with rate
      <a href="#" class="client-link">Lone Star HVAC &amp; Air</a>
      for transparent flat-rate pricing across the metro.
    </p>
    <p class="body-copy">
      The difference, technicians told us, comes down to airflow and refrigerant charge &mdash; not horsepower.
    </p>
    <div class="tag-pill">
      <span class="diamond">&#11045;</span> Your client&rsquo;s contextual link
    </div>
  </article>
</div>

<style>
  .clipping-wrap { position: relative; }
  .shadow-card {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 18px -10px -16px 26px;
    background: var(--ink);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }
  .card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--paper-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 26px 28px 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px -22px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
  }
  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .masthead {
    font-family: var(--f-display);
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .byline {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8A8475;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  .headline {
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 25px;
    line-height: 1.18;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .body-copy {
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.62;
    color: #3A352E;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }
  .body-copy:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .client-link {
    color: var(--red);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #E7B7AC;
    padding-bottom: 1px;
  }
  .tag-pill {
    margin-top: 18px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: #F5F1E8;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .diamond { color: var(--gold); }
</style>
